        "name": "Veil Of Spirits",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You draw on the essence of spiritual energy surrounding you to manifest a misty veil. When a creature that isn\u2019t immune to spirit damage begins its turn within the area, it must attempt a Reflex save. You can Dismiss the veil.",
